*salute* Fan Works Library, you have served us well. The tomes confined within your link addresses may forever be immortalised here in scriptures of underlined blue, providing delight to the next generation of kerbal readers and writers. If your legacy were to end here we shall not rest the blame with you...

...that said, Phase 2 would be an incredible project for someone, or perhaps a somemany, to embark upon!
